  "description": "Tax and reporting rules for employers providing coal to miners",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>As an employer, you don’t have to report or pay tax and national insurance on any reasonable amount of free coal – or payments in place of free coal – you give to miners working for you.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>This covers any employee who works at your colliery, except those working in clerical, administrative or technical roles.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"technical-guidance\">Technical guidance</h2>\n\n<p>The following guides contain more detailed information:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/eimanual/eim66690.htm\" title=\"Tax treatment of mineworkers: payments in lieu of free coal\">tax treatment of mineworkers: payments in lieu of free coal</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/nimmanual/nim02095.htm\" title=\"Class 1 National Insurance: payments to miners\">Class 1 National Insurance: payments to miners</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/manuals/nimmanual/nim14310.htm\" title=\"Class 1A National Insurance: extra-statutory concessions\">Class 1A National Insurance: extra-statutory concessions</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
